Note: Only auto attacks, Water Gun, Snipe Shot and Liquidation can critically Strike. Inteleon's Critical-Hit rate increases at levels 1 and 9. Critical hits deal 250% damage instead of 200%. At level 5, Inteleon gains 12.5% spell vamp (restores HP when dealing Special Attack damage).

Sobble

Evolves At 5

Drizzile

Evolves At 7

Sniper

Passive Ability

When this Pokémon stays near a wall for 1s it becomes camouflaged, making opposing Pokémon unable to target it, and starts gaining critical counters (up to a maximum of 3). While camouflaged, Inteleon is slowed by 10%. A critical counter is gained as soon as Inteleon is camouflaged, with a new counter gained every 3s while camouflaged. Dealing or receiving damage prevents Inteleon from starting to camouflage for 3s. When a critical counter is consumed, Inteleon's next attack or move that can critically strike is guaranteed to be a critical hit.

Critical hits deal 250% rather than 200% damage.

Attack

Auto Attack

Becomes a boosted attack with every third attack, dealing increased damage with 20% increased critical-hit rate.

48.2% SpA + 4 x (Level - 1) + 90

54.8% SpA + 6 x (Level - 1) + 100

Tearful Look

Move 1

8.00s Debuff

Decreases the Attack and Sp. Atk of the target Pokémon by 20% for 3s. Inteleon gains a critical counter and increases its movement speed by 40% for 3s (decreasing over time).

Tearful Look Upgrade Choices

Fell Stinger

6.50s Dash

Inteleon fires a sharp stinger in the designated direction. The stinger stops at the first Pokémon hit or when it reaches a wall. Inteleon gains two critical counters if either a Pokémon is hit or a wall is hit. If it hits a Pokémon it deals damage. If it hits a wall, this move's cooldown is reduced by half and Inteleon is pulled to the wall and starts camouflaging.

63% SpA + 5 x (Level - 1) + 200

Reduces this move's cooldown by 1s.

Acrobatics

7.50s Dash

Inteleon glides in the designated direction. If it hits a Pokémon or a wall, it can glide in a designated direction a second time. If Inteleon hits a Pokémon while gliding, Inteleon deals damage to it and decreases its movement speed by 30% for 2s. Every time Inteleon glides in a designated direction, it gains a critical counter. If Inteleon bounces off a wall or Pokémon, Liquidation's current cooldown is reduced by 2s.

This move can also be used while attacking with Liquidation.

54% SpA + 7 x (Level - 1) + 150

Increases the first glide's travel distance.

Water Gun

Move 2

7.50s Ranged

Inteleon squirts water, dealing damage to opposing Pokémon it hits.

27% SpA + 3 x (Level - 1) + 94

Water Gun Upgrade Choices

Snipe Shot

7.50s Ranged

Inteleon aims for up to 6s and then fires, dealing damage to opposing Pokémon it hits while partially ignoring their Sp. Def. by 15%/20%/25% depending on distance (close, mid, far respectively). Aiming reduces the possible spread of the shot, reaching maximum precision after aiming for 1.25s. The farther away the user is from the Pokémon it hits, the more damage it does. A maximum of three uses can be kept in reserve for this move. There is a 1.5s cooldown between uses.

61% SpA + 4 x (Level - 1) + 182

90% SpA + 8 x (Level - 1) + 270

121% SpA + 10 x (Level - 1) + 362

Reduces the cooldown for charges by 1s.

Liquidation

6.00s Sure Hit

Inteleon starts firing water projectiles at the designated Pokémon. Inteleon fires a total of 8 projectiles in 1.7s and is slowed by 60% while firing. Water projectiles can hit targets other than the designated Pokémon and only deal damage to the first Pokémon they hit. If this move hits the same Pokémon 5 times in a short time, Inteleon will deal 20% increased damage to this Pokémon for 3s.

14.2% SpA + 1 x (Level - 1) + 44

Increases the number of projectiles shot during the duration to 10.

Azure Spy Vision

Unite Move

112s 100000 Buff

Unlocks at level 9

For 10.5s, Inteleon can see nearby Pokémon that are in stealth or hiding in tall grass.

While active, also doubles Inteleon's critical-hit rate, and gives 1 critical counter per second.

Unite Buffs (6s duration):

20% Max HP Shield, 30% Movement Speed, 35% Attack Speed
